prodNameC: 卡蒂雅沙眼披衣菌IgG抗體檢測試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
1.Chlamydia(strain LGV II) antigen coated microassay plate.
2.Serum Diluent Type I: contains proclin(0.1%) as a preservative.
3.Cutoff calibrator (Calibrator): human serum or defibrinated plasma.
4.High positive Control: human serum or defibrinated plasma.
5.Low positive control: human serum or defibrinated plasma.
6.Negative control: human serum or defibrinated.
7.Horseradish-peroxidase(HRP) Conjugate: Goat anti-human IgG.
8.Chromogen/Substrate Solution Type I: Tetramethylbenzidine(TMB).
9.Wash Buffer Type I (20x concentrate): contains TBS, Tween-20 and proclin (0.1%) as preservative.
10.Stop Solution: contains a 1 N H2SO4 solution.
applicantAddr: 新北市板橋區民生路一段三三號六樓之五
efficacy: 檢測人體血清中披衣菌屬抗原之抗體 IgG。

mdKind.mdKindMCodeName: C 免疫學及微生物學用裝置
